I'm no groveling

12
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,230
supplicant,

13
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,510
yet no one

14
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:49,080
in this world has ever

15
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,600
understood me

16
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,480
or loved me.

17
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,790
Still, I cannot be called defeated.

18
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,000
From this day forward,

19
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:01,360
you will never forget Rongyang.

20
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,680
Father!

21
00:02:20,270 --> 00:02:25,230
♪Life is like flowers,
blooming and fading with the seasons♪

22
00:02:26,780 --> 00:02:31,410
♪Wind leaves marks,
swaying in the breeze♪

23
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:35,480
♪I don't wish for favors from the heavens♪

24
00:02:35,690 --> 00:02:38,140
♪To enjoy a blessed life♪

25
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:45,160
♪I only wish to be unburdened♪

26
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:50,770
♪Fate's been written; we're its slaves♪

27
00:02:52,490 --> 00:02:57,090
♪I dare not look back
at the road I came from♪

28
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:01,270
♪As the sun sets, the wise seek redemption♪

29
00:03:01,270 --> 00:03:04,320
♪I only wish to wake up one day♪

30
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:10,450
♪I won't lose with myself in the game♪

31
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:16,830
♪Alas, is it too late
to stop indulging myself♪

32
