634
00:37:56,470 --> 00:37:59,650
♪I fear that we'll part again♪

635
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:03,360
I dreamed of holding you like this

636
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:04,480
a million times,

637
00:38:06,710 --> 00:38:08,440
but every time I woke up,

638
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:09,960
